---
// Hero section — top of the main content area
---

<section class="hero" id="overview">
  <div class="hero-eyebrow">🔧 Engineering Documentation</div>
  <h1>
    Harness Engineering:<br /><span>Teaching AI Agents to Work Autonomously</span>
  </h1>
  <p class="hero-tagline">From chatting with agents to managing them.</p>
  <blockquote class="hero-quote">
    &ldquo;Anytime you find an agent makes a mistake, you take the time to engineer a solution
    such that the agent never makes that mistake again.&rdquo;
    <cite>&mdash; Mitchell Hashimoto</cite>
  </blockquote>
  <div class="hero-stats">
    <div>
      <div class="hero-stat-num">6</div>
      <div class="hero-stat-label">Phases Complete</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="hero-stat-num">100%</div>
      <div class="hero-stat-label">Harness Coverage</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="hero-stat-num">&infin;</div>
      <div class="hero-stat-label">Mistakes Prevented</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e3a5f 50%, #0f2744 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 72px 64px 64px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -60px;
    right: -60px;
    width: 400px;
    height: 400px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .hero-eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.12);
    border: 1px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.25);
    border-radius: 100px;
    padding: 5px 14px;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--sidebar-active);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 44px);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .hero h1 span {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), var(--teal));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }
  .hero-tagline {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: #94a3b8;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .hero-quote {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
    border-radius: 0 var(--radius-sm) var(--radius-sm) 0;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    max-width: 680px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #cbd5e1;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .hero-quote cite {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 8px;
    font-style: normal;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }
  .hero-stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: 40px;
    margin-top: 40px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .hero-stat-num {
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: white;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .hero-stat-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #64748b;
    margin-top: 4px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
</style>
